column5: I am looking for a hook up on the evening of Aug 30. I can travel an hour in any direction to do this. So if there is anyone who wants to go fishing on Monday night, let me know, via PM or post.
If it's a hook-up you're looking for, the Mozee is probably your surest bet.  As long as you don't mind spending a little money that is.
Not the type I am looking for.....
I'm 20 minutes away... and will see what I can do.  Randy
That sounds like a plan....BTW ask anyone, I am HORRIBLE company. Just so ya know.
Gee, thanks for the support dan...
